# Raphael Bekele — Personal Portfolio Website

This project is my personal portfolio site built using **Node.js**, **Express.js**, and **EJS** templating.  
It showcases my work, background, and contact information in a modern, minimal design inspired by Apple’s website aesthetic.

---

## live demo
View Portfolio on Render: https://js-portfolio-fmq6.onrender.com

---

- **Backend:** Node.js, Express.js  
- **Frontend:** EJS (Embedded JavaScript templates), Bootstrap 5, Font Awesome  
- **Styling:** Custom CSS (`public/stylesheets/style.css`)  
- **Hosting:** Render  
- **Version Control:** Git & GitHub

---

##  Project Structure
-js-portfolio/
-- app.js # Main server file (Express app)
--bin/www # Server start script
--package.json # Node project metadata
--public/
images/ # Profile and asset images
javascripts/ # Client-side JS files
 stylesheets/ # CSS styles (main: style.css)
routes/
index.js # Express routes for all pages
views/
layout.ejs # Shared layout (header, footer)
home.ejs # Homepage
 about.ejs # About Me page
 projects.ejs # Projects page
 contact.ejs # Contact page
 error.ejs # Error view (404 / server errors)


---

## Installation & Setup

### Clone repository
git clone https://github.com/raphaelbek04/js-portfolio.git
cd js-portfolio


 npm install

 npm start